The street, divided into multiple lanes by white lines, is filled with cars and buses, indicating a busy time of day. Overhead, power lines crisscross against the backdrop of a clear blue sky. In the distance, buildings rise, adding to the city's skyline. The sun shines brightly, casting a warm glow over the scene.
